reduceddescription: Freestyle 3 is the third installment of a dashboard replacement written by teamFSD. It allows users to list their games and homebrew which can be stored on various media. F3 is skinnable and highly adjustable to every users liking.
description:
Take your modded Xbox 360 to the next level with this third installment of the most popular dashboard replacement created by teamFSD. Automatically scan your harddrives for playable games and homebrew. Choose your own wallpapers, customize the menus to your liking, or even create your own skins! Play together with friends accross the world on LiNK using F3 in combination with Freestyle Plugin and link.JQE360.com. Get real time game info via WebUI, or add notes to the screencaptures you took while playing your favorite game!
Some Freestyle 3 features:
  • Coverflow title menu
  • Stylable menus
  • Custom wallpapers
  • Automatic title scanning
  • FTP Server
  • SMB Server
  • Webserver
  • Weather info
  • File manager
  • Fully reskinnable
In combination with Freestyle Plugin:
  • LiNK with HUD
  • In game screen captures
  • Web interface (including system info and notes on screencaptures)
